snippet.title: S30 Cinematic Trailer - Operation: Eruditio Rescue
snippet.description:
S30 Cinematic Trailer
Operation: Eruditio Rescue

While on patrol during the Festival of Enlightenment, Layla and the Eruditio Rangers encountered a sudden disturbance. Working together, they successfully protected the city once more...

Yet amidst these intricate events, a shrouded maestro was stepping into the spotlight...
